6 An Act relating to wildlife; amending 29 O.S. 2021,
Section 7-304, as amended by Section 1, Chapter 19,
7 O.S.L. 2022 (29 O.S. Supp. 2024, Section 7-304),
which relates to wildlife refuges and Wildlife
8 Management Areas; requiring nonresident hunters to
receive permission from the Oklahoma Wildlife
9 Conservation Commission to use certain areas;
authorizing the Commission to create certain system
10 for permitting; requiring permit fee; providing for
promulgation of rules; updating statutory language;
11 and providing an effective date.
