13
14 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
15 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY 29 O.S. 2021, Section 7-304, as
16 amended by Section 1, Chapter 19, O.S.L. 2022 (29 O.S. Supp. 2024,
17 Section 7-304), is amended to read as follows:
18 Section 7-304. A. Except as otherwise provided by law, no
19 person may enter upon any state or federal wildlife refuge or
20 Wildlife Management Area with a dog, a gun, or a bow.
21 B. Exceptions to the above provisions are when the Oklahoma
22 Wildlife Conservation Commission and/or the Oklahoma Tourism and
23 Recreation Commission may by resolution permit:
